divs: Sighting DetailsApril 4th--2010--1:30 AM--in Valrico F+l. I went outside to the front of my house-as I do every night to look for shooting stars. I was there about 10 min. when a noticed a strange light. It got closer and bigger so I ran and got my camera and took a picture. Thats it. I have no idea what it was. It was gone as fast as it appeared!
